#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"This release fixes `CVE 2019-12243 </news/security/istio-"
"security-2019-001>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:16
msgid "Bug fixes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"Fix issue where two gateways with overlapping hosts, created at the same "
"second, can cause Pilot to fail to generate routes correctly and lead to "
"Envoy listeners stuck indefinitely at startup in a warming state."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:22
msgid ""
"Improve the robustness of the SDS node agent: if Envoy sends a SDS "
"request with an empty ``ResourceNames``, ignore it and wait for the next "
"request instead of closing the connection (`Issue 13853 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/13853>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:26
msgid ""
"In prior releases Pilot automatically injected the experimental "
"``envoy.filters.network.mysql_proxy`` filter into the outbound filter "
"chain if the service port name is ``mysql``. This was surprising and "
"caused issues for some operators, so Pilot will now automatically inject "
"the ``envoy.filters.network.mysql_proxy`` filter only if the "
"``PILOT_ENABLE_MYSQL_FILTER`` environment variable is set to ``1`` "
"(`Issue 13998 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/13998>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:33
msgid ""
"Fix issue where Mixer policy checks were incorrectly disabled for TCP "
"(`Issue 13868 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/13868>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:37
msgid "Small enhancements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:39
msgid ""
"Add ``--applicationPorts`` option to the ``ingressgateway`` Helm charts. "
"When set to a comma-delimited list of ports, readiness checks will fail "
"until all the ports become active. When configured, traffic will not be "
"sent to Envoys stuck in the warming state."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.1.x/announcing-1.1.7/index.rst:43
msgid ""
"Increase memory limit in the ``ingressgateway`` Helm chart to 1GB and add"
" resource ``request`` and ``limits`` to the SDS node agent container to "
"support HPA autoscaling."
msgstr ""

